title: Inox Wind bags 201 MW project from Integrum Energy
description: Inox Wind CEO Kailash Tarachandani said, "Integrum has been a longstanding partner for us, and we are delighted that they have reaffirmed their faith in our product and solutions with this large equipment supply order for 201 MW".
